# Gate MCP server definitions for mcporter (pipe-separated)
# Format: name|type|endpoint|auth_type|description
# auth_type: api_key_secret | oauth | x_api_key | none
gate|stdio|npx -y gate-mcp|api_key_secret|Local CEX (stdio, API Key/Secret)
gate-cex-pub|http|https://api.gatemcp.ai/mcp|none|Remote CEX Public (no auth)
gate-cex-ex|http|https://api.gatemcp.ai/mcp/exchange|oauth|Remote CEX Exchange (Gate OAuth2)
gate-dex|http|https://api.gatemcp.ai/mcp/dex|x_api_key|DEX Operations
gate-dex-sec|http|https://api.gatemcp.ai/mcp/dex/sec|none|Gate Verify (tx check-in before DEX signing)
gate-info|http|https://api.gatemcp.ai/mcp/info|none|Info & Analysis
gate-news|http|https://api.gatemcp.ai/mcp/news|none|News Feed
gatepay-local-mcp|stdio|npx -y gatepay-local-mcp|gatepay_env|Gate Pay x402 (stdio; env placeholders — see gate-pay-x402)
gatepay-merchant-discovery|http|http://dev.halftrust.xyz/pay-mcp-server/mcp|none|Gate Pay merchant catalog (discoveryResource)
